9ebe7cf2ccfc.jpg 640w,https://cdn1.img.sputnikglobe.com/img/107843/74/1078437449_0:52:641:412_1280x0_80_0_0_c329ef1bbd01ae48d3c8409f1e04e44f.jpg 1280w,https://cdn1.img.sputnikglobe.com/img/107843/74/1078437449_0:52:641:412_1920x0_80_0_0_2bc21751c1b7b53a9f01b11e8d4950c3.jpg 1920w" referrerpolicy="no-referrer"></div></div><div class="media__copyright " data-nosnippet=""><div class="media__copyright-item m-copyright"> <a href="https://creativecommons.org/licenses/by-sa/2.0/" title="CC BY-SA 2.0">CC BY-SA 2.0</a> / <a href="https://www.flickr.com/photos/fillmorephotography/" title="迈克尔陈/Flickr">Michael Chen/Flickr</a> / </div></div></div></div><div class="article__messengers"><div class="flex-align_center"><span class="article__google-news__label"></span></div><div class="flex-align_center"></div><div class="article__telegram-news flex-align_center"><span class="article__google-news__label">订阅</span></div><div class="flex-align_center"><div class="article__telegram-button"><a href="https://t.me/SputnikInt" title="国际的" class="" target="_blank" rel="noopener nofollow">国际的</a></div><div class="article__telegram-button"><a href="https://telegram.me/sputniknewsindia" title="印度" class="" target="_blank" rel="noopener nofollow">印度</a></div><div class="article__telegram-button"><a href="https://t.me/sputnik_africa" title="非洲" class="" target="_blank" rel="noopener nofollow">非洲</a></div></div></div><div class="article__announce-text">据华盛顿（人造卫星）网报道：美国媒体周三报道，由于供应链问题和制造停工，美国正面临创纪录的抗癌药物短缺和其他危及生命的疾病。 </div></div><div class="article__body"><div class="article__block" data-type="text"><div class="article__text">报告称，抗癌药物是数百种短缺药物之一，其中还包括心脏搭桥手术药物、抗生素和儿童泰诺。</div></div><div class="article__block" data-type="text"><div class="article__text">报告补充说，治疗肺癌、乳腺癌、膀胱癌和卵巢癌的通用化疗形式也加剧了人们的担忧。</div></div><div class="article__block" data-type="text"><div class="article__text">报告称，鉴于面临短缺的化疗药物数量，约翰霍普金斯医学院教授阿曼达费德称这种情况为“公共卫生紧急情况”。</div></div><div class="article__block" data-type="text"><div class="article__text">报告称，白宫和国会正在关注摇摇欲坠的仿制药市场，该市场约占国内处方药的 90%。</div></div><div class="article__block" data-type="text"><div class="article__text">报道补充说，拜登政府还组建了一个团队，以减少药品供应链对来自印度和中国的药品和药物成分的严重依赖。</div></div></div> ]]>;</description><pubDate> Wed, 17 May 2023 19:21:18 GMT</pubDate><guid ispermalink="false"> https://sputniknews.com/20230517/us-drug-shortage-nears-record-high-amid-supply-chain-disruptions---reports-1110425572.html</guid><link/> https://sputniknews.com/20230517/us-drug-shortage-nears-record-high-amid-supply-chain-disruptions---reports-1110425572.html<category>美洲</category><category>我们</category><category>药品</category><category>处方药</category><category>药物运输</category></item><item><title><![CDATA[G7 Summit Kicks Off in Hiroshima, Japan]]></title><description><![CDATA[<div class="article__header"><div class="article__messengers"><div class="flex-align_center"><span class="article__google-news__label"></span></div><div class="flex-align_center"></div><div class="article__telegram-news flex-align_center"><span class="article__google-news__label">订阅</span></div><div class="flex-align_center"><div class="article__telegram-button"><a href="https://t.me/SputnikInt" title="国际的" class="" target="_blank" rel="noopener nofollow">国际的</a></div><div class="article__telegram-button"><a href="https://telegram.me/sputniknewsindia" title="印度" class="" target="_blank" rel="noopener nofollow">印度</a></div><div class="article__telegram-button"><a href="https://t.me/sputnik_africa" title="非洲" class="" target="_blank" rel="noopener nofollow">非洲</a></div></div></div><div class="article__announce-text">七国集团领导人将于 5 月 19 日至 21 日在日本举行会议，讨论当前的地缘政治和经济挑战——即在乌克兰危机和对俄罗斯制裁的情况下北约的扩张。 </div></div><div class="article__body"><div class="article__block" data-type="text"><div class="article__text">今年的 G7 会议点具有黑暗的象征意义——1945 年 8 月，美国用核武器轰炸了广岛，立即造成数十万人死亡，并将这座曾经繁荣的城市变成了一座放射性墓地。</div></div><div class="article__block" data-type="text"><div class="article__text">美国是唯一一个在战斗中使用过核武器的国家，历史学家一致认为，这一举动对苏联来说更像是一场奇观，而不是战术上必要的一步。</div></div><div class="article__block" data-type="text"><div class="article__text">然而，日本收起骄傲，拥抱西方价值观，成为美国的亲密盟友，随波逐流。现在世界上最大的墓地之一将举办一次关于北约东扩的峰会。 </div></div><div class="article__block" data-type="infographics"><div class="article__infographics-media  m-border" data-uid="1110421293"><div class="article__infographics_variant" data-type="desktop"><img media-type="hires" data-source-sid="sputnik_infographics" alt="G7 Summit in Hiroshima - Sputnik International" title="G7广岛峰会" src="https://cdn1.img.sputnikglobe.com/images/07e7/05/11/1110420422.png" referrerpolicy="no-referrer"></div><div class="article__infographics_variant" data-type="mobile"><img media-type="hires" data-source-sid="sputnik_infographics" alt="G7 Summit in Hiroshima - Sputnik International" title="G7广岛峰会" src="https://cdn1.img.sputnikglobe.com/images/07e7/05/11/1110420422.png" referrerpolicy="no-referrer"></div></div></div><div class="article__block" data-type="infographics"><div class="article__infographics-media  m-border" data-uid="1110421296"><div class="article__infographics_variant" data-type="desktop"><img media-type="hires" data-source-sid="sputnik_infographics" alt="G7 Summit in Hiroshima - Sputnik International" title="G7广岛峰会" src="https://cdn1.img.sputnikglobe.com/images/07e7/05/11/1110420596.png" referrerpolicy="no-referrer"></div><div class="article__infographics_variant" data-type="mobile"><img media-type="hires" data-source-sid="sputnik_infographics" alt="G7 Summit in Hiroshima - Sputnik International" title="G7广岛峰会" src="https://cdn1.img.sputnikglobe.com/images/07e7/05/11/1110420596.png" referrerpolicy="no-referrer"></div></div></div><div class="article__block" data-type="infographics"><div class="article__infographics-media  m-border" data-uid="1110421299"><div class="article__infographics_variant" data-type="desktop"><img media-type="hires" data-source-sid="sputnik_infographics" alt="G7 Summit in Hiroshima - Sputnik International" title="G7广岛峰会" src="https://cdn1.img.sputnikglobe.com/images/07e7/05/11/1110420770.png" referrerpolicy="no-referrer"></div><div class="article__infographics_variant" data-type="mobile"><img media-type="hires" data-source-sid="sputnik_infographics" alt="G7 Summit in Hiroshima - Sputnik International" title="G7广岛峰会" src="https://cdn1.img.sputnikglobe.com/images/07e7/05/11/1110420770.png" referrerpolicy="no-referrer"></div></div></div><div class="article__block" data-type="infographics"><div class="article__infographics-media  m-border" data-uid="1110421902"><div class="article__infographics_variant" data-type="desktop"><img media-type="hires" data-source-sid="sputnik_infographics" alt="G7 Summit in Hiroshima - Sputnik International" title="G7广岛峰会" src="https://cdn1.img.sputnikglobe.com/images/07e7/05/11/1110420947.png" referrerpolicy="no-referrer"></div><div class="article__infographics_variant" data-type="mobile"><img media-type="hires" data-source-sid="sputnik_infographics" alt="G7 Summit in Hiroshima - Sputnik International" title="G7广岛峰会" src="https://cdn1.img.sputnikglobe.com/images/07e7/05/11/1110420947.png" referrerpolicy="no-referrer"></div></div></div><div class="article__block" data-type="infographics"><div class="article__infographics-media  m-border" data-uid="1110421905"><div class="article__infographics_variant" data-type="desktop"><img media-type="hires" data-source-sid="sputnik_infographics" alt="G7 Summit in Hiroshima - Sputnik International" title="G7广岛峰会" src="https://cdn1.img.sputnikglobe.com/images/07e7/05/11/1110421121.png" referrerpolicy="no-referrer"></div><div class="article__infographics_variant" data-type="mobile"><img media-type="hires" data-source-sid="sputnik_infographics" alt="G7 Summit in Hiroshima - Sputnik International" title="G7广岛峰会" src="https://cdn1.img.sputnikglobe.com/images/07e7/05/11/1110421121.png" referrerpolicy="no-referrer"></div></div></div></div> ]]>;</description><pubDate> Wed, 17 May 2023 19:15:54 GMT</pubDate><guid ispermalink="false"> https://sputniknews.com/20230517/g7-summit-kicks-off-in-hiroshima-japan-1110421292.html</guid><link/> https://sputniknews.com/20230517/g7-summit-kicks-off-in-hiroshima-japan-1110421292.html<category>多媒体</category><category>资料图</category></item><item><title><![CDATA[Kinzhal Missile Strike Destroyed Five Patriot Launchers in Kiev - Russia]]></title><description><![CDATA[<div class="article__header"><div class="article__announce"><div class="media" data-media-tipe="ar16x9"><div class="media__size"><div class="photoview__open" data-photoview-group="1110424974" data-photoview-src="https://cdn1.img.sputnikglobe.com/img/107919/12/1079191229_0:0:2656:1659_1440x900_80_0_1_afbd596ff3b23cf9df56a79d07dc2631.jpg?source-sid=rian_photo" data-photoview-image-id="1079191227" data-photoview-sharelink="https://sputnikglobe.com/20230517/kinzhal-missile-strike-destroyed-five-patriot-launchers-in-kiev---russia-1110424974.html?share-img=1079191227"><noindex><div class="photoview__open-info"> <span class="photoview__copyright">© Sputnik / Алексей Майшев</span><span class="photoview__desc-text">装备 Kinzhal 的 MiG-31 在飞越克里姆林宫期间重复即将到来的胜利大阅兵，2020 年 5 月 4 日。</span> </div></noindex><img media-type="ar16x9" data-source-sid="rian_photo" alt="Kinzhal-armed MiG-31s during their flight past the Kremlin amid the repetition for the upcoming Victory Parade, May 4, 2020. - Sputnik International, 1920, 17.05.2023" title="2020 年 5 月 4 日，Kinzhal 武装的 MiG-31 在飞越克里姆林宫期间重复举行胜利大阅兵。" src="https://cdn1.img.sputnikglobe.com/img/107919/12/1079191229_0:0:2656:1495_1920x0_80_0_0_1272e2f0dd5fe6480298c714834798a5.jpg" decoding="async" width="1920" height="1080" srcset="https://cdn1.img.sputnikglobe.com/img/107919/12/1079191229_0:0:2656:1495_640x0_80_0_0_152e7e056668a9a88a3cddac7d48c2e5.jpg 640w,https://cdn1.img.sputnikglobe.com/img/107919/12/1079191229_0:0:2656:1495_1280x0_80_0_0_88c13eec1cb6a773644cb740301af4de.jpg 1280w,https://cdn1.img.sputnikglobe.com/img/107919/12/1079191229_0:0:2656:1495_1920x0_80_0_0_1272e2f0dd5fe6480298c714834798a5.jpg 1920w" referrerpolicy="no-referrer"></div></div><div class="media__copyright " data-nosnippet=""><div class="media__copyright-item m-copyright"> © Sputnik / Алексей Майшев</div> / </div></div></div><div class="article__messengers"><div class="flex-align_center"><span class="article__google-news__label"></span></div><div class="flex-align_center"></div><div class="article__telegram-news flex-align_center"><span class="article__google-news__label">订阅</span></div><div class="flex-align_center"><div class="article__telegram-button"><a href="https://t.me/SputnikInt" title="国际的" class="" target="_blank" rel="noopener nofollow">国际的</a></div><div class="article__telegram-button"><a href="https://telegram.me/sputniknewsindia" title="印度" class="" target="_blank" rel="noopener nofollow">印度</a></div><div class="article__telegram-button"><a href="https://t.me/sputnik_africa" title="非洲" class="" target="_blank" rel="noopener nofollow">非洲</a></div></div></div><div class="article__announce-text">据莫斯科（人造卫星）网报道：虽然基辅声称已经拦截了六枚 Kinzhals，但俄罗斯国防部长谢尔盖绍伊古在接受人造卫星采访时告诉人造卫星，乌克兰的报道在各个方面都是错误的，并指出只有几枚俄罗斯导弹足以穿透基辅的防御系统。 </div></div><div class="article__body"><div class="article__block" data-type="quote"><div class="article__quote"><div class="article__quote-text"><p> “根据经核实的信息，由于<a href="https://sputnikglobe.com/20230517/unstoppable-kinzhal-one-us-made-patriot-cracked-up-more-to-come-1110424287.html" target="_blank">Kinzhal 高超音速导弹系统对基辅市的一次袭击</a>，一个多功能雷达站以及美国制造的爱国者防空导弹系统的五个发射器被击中并完全2023 年 5 月 16 日被摧毁，”俄罗斯国防部说。 </p></div><div class="article__quote-info"><div class="elem-info"><div class="elem-info__share"><div class="share" data-id="1110424974" data-url="https://sputnikglobe.com/20230517/kinzhal-missile-strike-destroyed-five-patriot-launchers-in-kiev---russia-1110424974.html?share-block=1110424975" data-title="&amp;quot;According to verified information, as a result of a strike by the Kinzhal hypersonic missile system in the city of Kiev a multifunctional radar station, as well as five launchers of the Patriot anti-aircraft missile system manufactured by the United States were hit and completely destroyed on May 16, 2023,&amp;quot; the Russian Defense Ministry said."></div></div></div></div></div></div><div class="article__block" data-type="text"><div class="article__text"> Kinzhal（直译“匕首”）是俄罗斯总统弗拉基米尔·普京于 2018 年 3 月公布的新型战略武器之一。它于 2017 年 12 月首次进入战斗值班，进行了广泛的飞行和战斗测试。这种具有核武器能力的武器是任何国家部署的第一种高超音速导弹系统。</div></div><div class="article__block" data-type="text"><div class="article__text"> Kinzhal 的射程超过 2,000 公里（1,200 英里）。它能够达到高达 10 马赫（12,250 公里/小时或 7,612 英里/小时）的速度，同时还能执行规避机动，这有助于 Kinzhal 几乎不受敌方空中导弹防御系统的伤害。</div></div></div> ]]>;</description><pubDate> Wed, 17 May 2023 19:01:31 GMT</pubDate><guid ispermalink="false"> https://sputniknews.com/20230517/kinzhal-missile-strike-destroyed-five-patriot-launchers-in-kiev---russia-1110424974.html</guid><link/> https://sputniknews.com/20230517/kinzhal-missile-strike-destroyed-five-patriot-launchers-in-kiev---russia-1110424974.html<category>俄罗斯在乌克兰的特别行动</category><category>Kinzhal 导弹系统</category><category>俄罗斯国防部</category><category>俄罗斯</category><category>乌克兰</category><category>乌克兰危机</category></item><item><title><![CDATA[Truss 'Cashing in' on Her Former UK Premiership With Superfluous Taiwan Speech]]></title><description><![CDATA[<div class="article__header"><div class="article__announce"><div class="media" data-media-tipe="ar16x9"><div class="media__size"><div class="photoview__open" data-photoview-group="1110424657" data-photoview-src="https://cdn1.img.sputnikglobe.com/img/07e7/05/11/1110413290_0:0:2915:1943_1440x900_80_0_1_0d6de5087db4d98e80a5f11e3966136d.jpg?source-sid=afp" data-photoview-image-id="1110413272" data-photoview-sharelink="https://sputnikglobe.com/20230517/truss-cashing-in-on-her-former-uk-premiership-with-superfluous-taiwan-speech-1110424657.html?share-img=1110413272"><noindex><div class="photoview__open-info"> <span class="photoview__copyright">© <a href="https://ria.ru/docs/about/copyright_afp.html" title="法新社 2023">AFP 2023</a> / I-HWA CHENG</span><span class="photoview__desc-text">英国前首相特拉斯于 2023 年 5 月 17 日在台北发表演讲，这是她对台湾进行为期五天访问的一部分</span></div></noindex><img media-type="ar16x9" data-source-sid="afp" alt="Britain's former prime minister Liz Truss delivers a speech as part of her five-day visit to Taiwan, in Taipei on May 17, 2023 - Sputnik International, 1920, 17.05.2023" title="2023 年 5 月 17 日，英国前首相利兹·特拉斯 (Liz Truss) 在台北对台湾进行为期五天的访问，并发表演讲" src="https://cdn1.img.sputnikglobe.com/img/07e7/05/11/1110413290_0:152:2915:1792_1920x0_80_0_0_a012196bacc40dbbfae21c307a9fd17b.jpg" decoding="async" width="1920" height="1080" srcset="https://cdn1.img.sputnikglobe.com/img/07e7/05/11/1110413290_0:152:2915:1792_640x0_80_0_0_fe4a638a244f4923680c56e83854fc5a.jpg 640w,https://cdn1.img.sputnikglobe.com/img/07e7/05/11/1110413290_0:152:2915:1792_1280x0_80_0_0_8e1a381dc85d5c8c6f02e1f7744eed49.jpg 1280w,https://cdn1.img.sputnikglobe.com/img/07e7/05/11/1110413290_0:152:2915:1792_1920x0_80_0_0_a012196bacc40dbbfae21c307a9fd17b.jpg 1920w" referrerpolicy="no-referrer"></div></div><div class="media__copyright " data-nosnippet=""><div class="media__copyright-item m-copyright"> © <a href="https://ria.ru/docs/about/copyright_afp.html" title="法新社 2023">AFP 2023</a> / I-HWA Cheng </div></div></div></div><div class="article__messengers"><div class="flex-align_center"><span class="article__google-news__label"></span></div><div class="flex-align_center"></div><div class="article__telegram-news flex-align_center"><span class="article__google-news__label">订阅</span></div><div class="flex-align_center"><div class="article__telegram-button"><a href="https://t.me/SputnikInt" title="国际的" class="" target="_blank" rel="noopener nofollow">国际的</a></div><div class="article__telegram-button"><a href="https://telegram.me/sputniknewsindia" title="印度" class="" target="_blank" rel="noopener nofollow">印度</a></div><div class="article__telegram-button"><a href="https://t.me/sputnik_africa" title="非洲" class="" target="_blank" rel="noopener nofollow">非洲</a></div></div></div><div class="article__author"><div class="article__author-item"><div class="article__author-wrapper"><div class="article__author-info"><div class="article__author-name">芳汀嘉迪尼耶</div><div class="article__author-links"><a class="m-color-main" href="https://sputniknews.com/author_gardinier_fantine/" title="所有材料">所有材料</a></div></div></div></div></div><div class="article__announce-text">一位台湾事务专家告诉人造卫星网，现在保守党议员和前总理利兹·特拉斯 (Liz Truss) 已经沦为一名立法者，对英国政策的影响力已经很小，她对台湾的挑衅性访问主要是在重复伦敦已经启动的政策。周三。 </div></div><div class="article__body"><div class="article__block" data-type="text"><div class="article__text">当天早些时候，英国保守党议员、前首相特拉斯访问中国台湾岛谴责北京， <a href="https://sputnikglobe.com/20230313/uk-domestic-spooks-to-fortify-businesses-against-chinese-and-russian-cyber-snooping-1108333174.html" target="_blank">指责中华人民共和国</a>应对与美国及其盟友的冷战负责。她还称赞由获得美国非正式支持的反叛势力统治的台湾是“对极权主义的持久谴责”，极权主义的命运是欧洲的“核心利益”。 </div></div><div class="article__block" data-type="quote"><div class="article__quote"><div class="article__quote-text"> “对台湾的封锁或入侵将破坏欧洲的自由和民主。正如俄罗斯在乌克兰的胜利会破坏太平洋地区的自由和民主一样，”特拉斯说。 “我们英国和自由世界必须竭尽全力支持你。” </div><div class="article__quote-info"><div class="elem-info"><div class="elem-info__share"><div class="share" data-id="1110424657" data-url="https://sputnikglobe.com/20230517/truss-cashing-in-on-her-former-uk-premiership-with-superfluous-taiwan-speech-1110424657.html?share-block=1110424659" data-title="“A blockade or invasion of Taiwan would undermine freedom and democracy in Europe. Just as a Russian victory in Ukraine would undermine freedom and democracy in the Pacific,” Truss said. “We in the United Kingdom and the free world must do all we can to back you.”"></div></div></div></div></div></div><div class="article__block" data-type="text"><div class="article__text">北京<u><a href="https://sputnikglobe.com/20230517/beijing-bashes-washed-up-british-politicians-as-truss-touts-china-as-threat-in-taiwan-1110413762.html" target="_blank">予以回击</a></u>，外交部表示，“过气的英国政客利用台湾来吸引人们对他们自己的关注。”此前，中国驻伦敦大使馆称特拉斯访华是“一场危险的政治秀，只会伤害英国”。</div></div><div class="article__block" data-type="text"><div class="article__text"><strong>政治风险分析师罗斯·法因戈尔德 (Ross Feingold) 拥有 20 多年为客户提供台湾政治风险建议的经验</strong>，他周三对人造卫星表示，英国“与美国一样，正在扩大‘支持朋友’和国内投资半导体行业。Truss 只是在谈论总理 [Rishi] Sunak 已经在做的部分事情。当然，政府外的人很容易呼吁政府加快行动。但一般来说，Sunak 可能不会去在这些问题上听取特拉斯的建议。” </div></div><div class="article__block" data-type="quote"><div class="article__quote"><div class="article__quote-text"><p> “2023 年 3 月 31 日，英国和全面进步跨太平洋伙伴关系谈判小组结束了<u><a href="https://sputnikglobe.com/20230331/uk-to-join-agreement-for-trans-pacific-partnership-1108981195.html">英国加入 CPTPP 的</a></u>谈判。英国似乎正在采纳特拉斯的建议，至少部分是为了与中国脱钩。然而，在5月初商务贸易部国务大臣多米尼克约翰逊访问香港，这是英国五年来第一位访问香港的部长。所以英国首相里希苏纳克似乎仍然想要香港（和推而广之，中国）将英国视为某些商品和服务的来源。” </p></div><div class="article__quote-info"><div class="elem-info"><div class="elem-info__share"><div class="share" data-id="1110424657" data-url="https://sputnikglobe.com/20230517/truss-cashing-in-on-her-former-uk-premiership-with-superfluous-taiwan-speech-1110424657.html?share-block=1110424662" data-title="&amp;quot;On 31 March 2023, the UK and Comprehensive and Progressive Trans-Pacific Partnership negotiating teams concluded negotiations for the UK&amp;#x27;s entry into the CPTPP. The UK seems to be taking Truss&amp;#x27;s advice at least in part to de-couple from China. However, in early May Dominic Johnson, Minister of State in the Department for Business and Trade, visited Hong Kong, which was the first British minister to visit Hong Kong in five years. So it seems that the UK Prime Minister Rishi Sunak still wants Hong Kong (and by extension, China) to look to the UK as a source for certain goods and services.&amp;quot;"></div></div></div></div></div></div><div class="article__block" data-type="text"><div class="article__text">总而言之，法因戈尔德表示，英国任期最短的首相在其政府垮台前仅上任七周，他访问该地区将被愤世嫉俗者视为“又一位前领导人或政府高级官员利用他们的权力获利”以前的政府角色。” </div></div><div class="article__block" data-type="quote"><div class="article__quote"><div class="article__quote-text"><p> “媒体报道称，特拉斯在 4 月份因在印度发表演讲而获得 65,000 英镑。鉴于特拉斯在英国的‘品牌形象’有多糟糕，印太地区的民众不太可能对她在台湾发表演讲有太多看法.中国官方媒体对特拉斯访问台湾的批评可能会给予它更多的关注。 </p></div><div class="article__quote-info"><div class="elem-info"><div class="elem-info__share"><div class="share" data-id="1110424657" data-url="https://sputnikglobe.com/20230517/truss-cashing-in-on-her-former-uk-premiership-with-superfluous-taiwan-speech-1110424657.html?share-block=1110424793" data-title="&amp;quot;Media reports state that in April, Truss received £65,000 for a speech in India. Given how bad the Truss ‘brand image’ is in the UK, it’s unlikely the population in the Indo Pacific will think much of her making a speech in Taiwan. The criticism by China state media of Truss&amp;#x27;s visit to Taiwan probably gives it more attention than it would otherwise have received.&amp;quot;"></div></div></div></div></div></div></div> ]]>;</description><pubDate> Wed, 17 May 2023 18:34:52 GMT</pubDate><guid ispermalink="false"> https://sputniknews.com/20230517/truss-cashing-in-on-her-former-uk-premiership-with-superfluous-taiwan-speech-1110424657.html</guid><link/> https://sputniknews.com/20230517/truss-cashing-in-on-her-former-uk-premiership-with-superfluous-taiwan-speech-1110424657.html<category>分析</category><category>台湾</category><category>利兹桁架</category><category>中国</category><category>冷战</category><category>英国</category></item><item><title><![CDATA[Unstoppable Kinzhal: One US-Made Patriot 'Cracked Up', More to Come]]></title><description><![CDATA[<div class="article__header"><div class="article__announce"><div class="media" data-media-tipe="ar16x9"><div class="media__size"><div class="photoview__open" data-photoview-group="1110424287" data-photoview-src="https://cdn1.img.sputnikglobe.com/img/07e7/02/14/1107605552_0:0:3185:2048_1440x900_80_0_1_f96c64d65f67c90b24c7f42bbfc25490.jpg?source-sid=rian_photo" data-photoview-image-id="1107605534" data-photoview-sharelink="https://sputnikglobe.com/20230517/unstoppable-kinzhal-one-us-made-patriot-cracked-up-more-to-come-1110424287.html?share-img=1107605534"><noindex><div class="photoview__open-info"> <span class="photoview__copyright">© Sputnik / Alexey Kudenko</span> <span class="photoview__desc-text">Kinzhal 导弹。档案照片</span></div></noindex><img media-type="ar16x9" data-source-sid="rian_photo" alt="A Kinzhal missile. File photo - Sputnik International, 1920, 17.05.2023" title="一枚 Kinzhal 导弹。档案照片" src="https://cdn1.img.sputnikglobe.com/img/07e7/02/14/1107605552_0:129:3185:1921_1920x0_80_0_0_f3d5f0091890e9b52102339998c5aed2.jpg" decoding="async" width="1920" height="1080" srcset="https://cdn1.img.sputnikglobe.com/img/07e7/02/14/1107605552_0:129:3185:1921_640x0_80_0_0_5aa8e2819954af3acfbc8aacd626ca2a.jpg 640w,https://cdn1.img.sputnikglobe.com/img/07e7/02/14/1107605552_0:129:3185:1921_1280x0_80_0_0_3d1310ac1a2a8cd2749bc4953797eb65.jpg 1280w,https://cdn1.img.sputnikglobe.com/img/07e7/02/14/1107605552_0:129:3185:1921_1920x0_80_0_0_f3d5f0091890e9b52102339998c5aed2.jpg 1920w" referrerpolicy="no-referrer"></div></div><div class="media__copyright " data-nosnippet=""><div class="media__copyright-item m-copyright"> © Sputnik / Alexey Kudenko</div> / </div></div></div><div class="article__messengers"><div class="flex-align_center"><span class="article__google-news__label"></span></div><div class="flex-align_center"></div><div class="article__telegram-news flex-align_center"><span class="article__google-news__label">订阅</span></div><div class="flex-align_center"><div class="article__telegram-button"><a href="https://t.me/SputnikInt" title="国际的" class="" target="_blank" rel="noopener nofollow">国际的</a></div><div class="article__telegram-button"><a href="https://telegram.me/sputniknewsindia" title="印度" class="" target="_blank" rel="noopener nofollow">印度</a></div><div class="article__telegram-button"><a href="https://t.me/sputnik_africa" title="非洲" class="" target="_blank" rel="noopener nofollow">非洲</a></div></div></div><div class="article__author"><div class="article__author-item"><div class="article__author-wrapper"><div class="article__author-info"><div class="article__author-name">叶卡捷琳娜布林诺娃</div><div class="article__author-links"><a class="m-color-main" href="https://sputniknews.com/author_ekaterina_blinova/" title="所有材料">所有材料</a> <a data-modal-open="feedback_author" href="mailto:e.blinova@sputniknews.com" title="写给作者">写给作者</a></div></div></div></div></div><div class="article__announce-text">俄罗斯用 Kinzhal 高超音速导弹击落驻扎在基辅的美制 MIM-104 爱国者地对空导弹 (SAM) 系统是莫斯科的公关妙招，军事中心的军事专家鲍里斯·罗任 (Boris Rozhin)政治新闻，告诉人造卫星，并补充说更多的爱国者可能很快也会被“破解”。 </div></div><div class="article__body"><div class="article__block" data-type="text"><div class="article__text">俄罗斯国防部 (MoD) 宣布，5 月 16 日，爱国者系统<a href="https://sputnikglobe.com/20230517/nutcracker-what-we-know-about-russias-kinzhal-hitting-us-patriot-system-in-kiev-1110418058.html" target="_blank">在基辅被 Kinzhal 高超音速弹道导弹</a>击中。</div></div><div class="article__block" data-type="text"><div class="article__text"> Kinzhal 发射是在俄罗斯武装部队“使用远程精确制导空基和海基武器对乌克兰武装部队 (AFU) 部队以及所提供的弹药、武器和军事装备库进行联合攻击的情况下进行的由西方国家，”声明说。目前，乌克兰军方拥有两个爱国者联合体。 </div></div><div class="article__block" data-type="quote"><div class="article__quote"><div class="article__quote-text"><p> “俄罗斯在形象方面取得了重要胜利，”罗任说。 “这表明这个 [爱国者] 综合体，尽管围绕它进行了所有公关大惊小怪，但非常脆弱，如果需要，俄罗斯可以将其禁用。（......）因此，在摧毁一个综合体后，俄罗斯将寻找下一个在那里。” </p></div><div class="article__quote-info"><div class="elem-info"><div class="elem-info__share"><div class="share" data-id="1110424287" data-url="https://sputnikglobe.com/20230517/unstoppable-kinzhal-one-us-made-patriot-cracked-up-more-to-come-1110424287.html?share-block=1110424289" data-title="&amp;quot;Russia scored an important victory for its image,&amp;quot; said Rozhin. &amp;quot;It showed that this [Patriot] complex, despite all the PR fuss around it, is quite vulnerable, and if desired, Russia can disable it. (…) And, accordingly, having destroyed one complex, Russia will look for the next ones that are there.&amp;quot;"></div></div></div></div></div></div><div class="article__block" data-type="text"><div class="article__text">据称俄罗斯 Kinzhal 导弹击中基辅爱国者防空系统的画面已经<a href="https://sputnikglobe.com/20230516/russias-kinzhal-missile-destroys-patriot-system-in-kiev-1110397858.html" target="_blank">在社交媒体上引起轰动</a>。</div></div><div class="article__block" data-type="text"><div class="article__text">视频中可以看到美国MIM-104爱国者防空系统电池极其密集的工作。一旦<a href="https://sputnikglobe.com/20230511/us-patriot-system-not-capable-of-intercepting-russian-kinzhal-missile---source-1110264588.html" target="_blank">防空系统用完导弹</a>，发射地点就会发生强烈爆炸。</div></div><div class="article__block" data-type="text"><div class="article__text">根据 Rozhin 的说法，有问题的镜头揭穿了基辅试图谎称“一切都很好”的谎言。西方主流媒体争先恐后地称，美制系统并没有被彻底打倒， <a href="https://sputnikglobe.com/20230517/us-reportedly-still-assessing-damage-to-patriot-system-after-russian-strike-on-kiev-1110412365.html" target="_blank">只是“受损”。</a>然而，根据军事专家的说法，很明显俄罗斯的空袭使爱国者无法作战，即使这个复杂综合体中只有一个元素被摧毁。他补充说，修复它需要很多时间和精力。 </div></div><div class="article__block" data-type="quote"><div class="article__quote"><div class="article__quote-text"><p> “俄罗斯国防部并不急于透露这次袭击是如何组织的，”罗任继续说道。 “显然，最初有各种无人机和导弹引诱包括爱国者在内的敌方防空系统工作，在确定了爱国者防空系统的特定作战区域后，它被 Kinzhal 高超音速系统击中。实际上，在博主发布的视频中，可以清楚地看到，在导弹击中爱国者阵地区域之前，显然，机组人员注意到目标不是基辅的某个物体，而是他们自己。进行了大规模的导弹发射[由爱国者]发射了 32 枚导弹拦截 Kinzhal，他们无法将其击落，因此，Kinzhal 击中了目标。” </p></div><div class="article__quote-info"><div class="elem-info"><div class="elem-info__share"><div class="share" data-id="1110424287" data-url="https://sputnikglobe.com/20230517/unstoppable-kinzhal-one-us-made-patriot-cracked-up-more-to-come-1110424287.html?share-block=1110424293" data-title="&amp;quot;The Russian Ministry of Defense is in no hurry to disclose how the attack was organized,&amp;quot; continued Rozhin. &amp;quot;Apparently, initially there were various drones and missiles that lured the work of enemy air defense systems, including the Patriot, and after a specific area of operation of the Patriot air defense system was identified, it was hit by the Kinzhal hypersonic system. Actually, in the footage published by the bloggers, it is clearly seen that before the missile hit the Patriot position area, apparently, the crew noticed that the target was not some object in Kiev, but themselves. A massive launch of missiles was carried out [by the Patriot], 32 missiles were fired to intercept the Kinzhal, they could not bring it down, and accordingly, the Kinzhal hit the target.&amp;quot;"></div></div></div></div></div></div><div class="article__block" data-type="text"><div class="article__text">这位军事专家指出，西方媒体将大规模导弹发射评估为爱国者号机组人员恐慌的迹象。也就是说，他们决定，如果他们同时发射所有导弹，那么，也许至少其中一枚会击中 Kinzhal。唉，他们所有的计算都被证明是错误的。</div></div><div class="article__block" data-type="text"><div class="article__text">一方面，这种情况被解读为乌克兰船员训练不足所致。另一方面，如果爱国者综合体由外国军队操作，西方看起来会更糟，这意味着机组人员未能拦截高超音速导弹显然使他们失去了数条北约军官或教官的生命，据罗任说。</div></div><div class="article__block" data-type="text"><div class="article__text">此外，上述镜头表明，即使是大规模发射导弹也<a href="https://sputnikglobe.com/20230510/fact-check-ukraine-didnt-shoot-down-russias-kinzhal-hypersonic-missile-1110235332.html" target="_blank">无法阻止 Kinzhal</a> 。这也表明爱国者已经过时了，这位军事专家回忆说，此前，沙特阿拉伯因美国制造的防空系统不符合规定的规格而受到严厉批评。 </div></div><div class="article__block" data-type="quote"><div class="article__quote"><div class="article__quote-text"><p> “爱国者是过去的系统，”罗任说。 “由于导弹数量众多，爱国者必须通过与其他系统（包括电子战系统和预警机）的相互作用来提供防空能力。默认情况下，它们应该击落飞机、巡航导弹和弹道导弹。爱国者 PAC -2 和爱国者 PAC-3 是目前​​在美国和各个国家/地区在世界范围内使用的两个主要版本。但即使在也门战争期间，很明显，即使据说 PAC-3 可以有效对抗伊朗巡航弹道导弹，一些被这些 [防空] 综合体覆盖的物体仍然被伊朗导弹击中。在这方面，爱国者对 1980 年代、1990 年代、2000 年代的飞机和导弹仍然非常有效。(...) [但是]爱国者没有任何对抗高超音速武器的手段。当这个综合体被创建时，没有这样的任务，“他总结道。 </p></div><div class="article__quote-info"><div class="elem-info"><div class="elem-info__share"><div class="share" data-id="1110424287" data-url="https://sputnikglobe.com/20230517/unstoppable-kinzhal-one-us-made-patriot-cracked-up-more-to-come-1110424287.html?share-block=1110424296" data-title="&amp;quot;The Patriot is a system of the past,&amp;quot; Rozhin said. &amp;quot;The Patriot must provide air defense due to a large number of missiles, through interaction with other systems, including electronic warfare systems, and AWACS aircraft. They should, by default, shoot down aircraft, cruise missiles, and ballistic missiles. The Patriot PAC-2 and the Patriot PAC-3 are the two main versions currently exploited around the world, in the US and various countries. But even during the war in Yemen, it became clear that even though the PAC-3 was said to be effective against Iranian cruise ballistic missiles, some objects that were covered by these [air defense] complexes were nonetheless hit by Iranian missiles. In this regard, the Patriot remains quite effective against aircraft and missiles of the 1980s, 1990s, 2000s. (…) [However] the Patriot does not have any means of fighting against hypersonic weapons. When this complex was created, there was no such a task,&amp;quot; he concluded."></div></div></div></div></div></div></div> ]]>;</description><pubDate> Wed, 17 May 2023 18:05:45 GMT</pubDate><guid ispermalink="false"> https://sputniknews.com/20230517/unstoppable-kinzhal-one-us-made-patriot-cracked-up-more-to-come-1110424287.html</guid><link/> https://sputniknews.com/20230517/unstoppable-kinzhal-one-us-made-patriot-cracked-up-more-to-come-1110424287.html<category>俄罗斯在乌克兰的特别行动</category><category>俄罗斯</category><category>俄罗斯国防部</category><category>乌克兰武装部队</category><category>基辅</category><category>乌克兰</category><category>爱国者</category><category>机载预警和控制系统 (AWACS)</category><category> Kinzhal 导弹系统</category><category>超音速导弹</category><category>高超音速武器</category><category>军事情报</category></item><item><title><![CDATA[Congress Inaction on Debt Limit 'Greatest Threat' to US Economy Since Pandemic - Treasury]]></title><description><![CDATA[<div class="article__header"><div class="article__announce"><div class="media" data-media-tipe="ar16x9"><div class="media__size"><div class="photoview__open" data-photoview-group="1110424452" data-photoview-src="https://cdn1.img.sputnikglobe.com/img/105550/74/1055507458_0:0:1920:1280_1440x900_80_0_1_044512ee5f3779694833e8b2814f0a59.jpg?source-sid=cc_0" data-photoview-image-id="1055507457" data-photoview-sharelink="https://sputnikglobe.com/20230517/congress-inaction-on-debt-limit-greatest-threat-to-us-economy-since-pandemic---treasury-1110424452.html?share-img=1055507457"><noindex><div class="photoview__open-info"> <span class="photoview__copyright"><a href="https://creativecommons.org/publicdomain/zero/1.0/" title="CC0">CC0</a> / /</span><span class="photoview__desc-text">美元</span></div></noindex><img media-type="ar16x9" data-source-sid="cc_0" alt="US Dollar - Sputnik International, 1920, 17.05.2023" title="美元" src="https://cdn1.img.sputnikglobe.com/img/105550/74/1055507458_0:100:1921:1180_1920x0_80_0_0_cee45ebbabcd54660562b88b922094a2.jpg" decoding="async" width="1920" height="1080" srcset="https://cdn1.img.sputnikglobe.com/img/105550/74/1055507458_0:100:1921:1180_640x0_80_0_0_5d1d13e0d45c3278dc28e4848b2ad521.jpg 640w,https://cdn1.img.sputnikglobe.com/img/105550/74/1055507458_0:100:1921:1180_1280x0_80_0_0_40516336a150e464a55681d394702144.jpg 1280w,https://cdn1.img.sputnikglobe.com/img/105550/74/1055507458_0:100:1921:1180_1920x0_80_0_0_cee45ebbabcd54660562b88b922094a2.jpg 1920w" referrerpolicy="no-referrer"></div></div><div class="media__copyright " data-nosnippet=""><div class="media__copyright-item m-copyright"> <a href="https://creativecommons.org/publicdomain/zero/1.0/" title="CC0">CC0</a> / / </div></div></div></div><div class="article__messengers"><div class="flex-align_center"><span class="article__google-news__label"></span></div><div class="flex-align_center"></div><div class="article__telegram-news flex-align_center"><span class="article__google-news__label">订阅</span></div><div class="flex-align_center"><div class="article__telegram-button"><a href="https://t.me/SputnikInt" title="国际的" class="" target="_blank" rel="noopener nofollow">国际的</a></div><div class="article__telegram-button"><a href="https://telegram.me/sputniknewsindia" title="印度" class="" target="_blank" rel="noopener nofollow">印度</a></div><div class="article__telegram-button"><a href="https://t.me/sputnik_africa" title="非洲" class="" target="_blank" rel="noopener nofollow">非洲</a></div></div></div><div class="article__announce-text">据华盛顿（人造卫星）网报道：美国财政部副部长沃利·阿德耶莫周三表示，美国国会无法通过提高债务上限来让美国履行其义务，这是自全球大流行以来美国经济面临的最大威胁。 </div></div><div class="article__body"><div class="article__block" data-type="quote"><div class="article__quote"><div class="article__quote-text"><p> “自大流行以来美国经济取得的进步面临的最大威胁是国会未能采取行动履行美国的义务，”阿德耶莫在 2023 年全国亚洲/太平洋岛民美国商会和创业大会上表示商业峰会。 </p></div><div class="article__quote-info"><div class="elem-info"><div class="elem-info__share"><div class="share" data-id="1110424452" data-url="https://sputnikglobe.com/20230517/congress-inaction-on-debt-limit-greatest-threat-to-us-economy-since-pandemic---treasury-1110424452.html?share-block=1110424453" data-title="&amp;quot;The single greatest threat to the progress the American economy has made since the pandemic is Congress&amp;#x27;s failure to take action to meet the United States’s obligations,&amp;quot; Adeyemo said at the National Asian / Pacific Islander American Chamber of Commerce and Entrepreneurship (National ACE) 2023 Business Summit."></div></div></div></div></div></div><div class="article__block" data-type="text"><div class="article__text">阿德耶莫警告说，不解除债务上限将导致该国陷入衰退。他补充说，这也会伤害小企业并引发一波公司倒闭潮。 </div></div><div class="article__block" data-type="quote"><div class="article__quote"><div class="article__quote-text"><p> “国会必须采取行动提高债务上限，并采取必要措施保护家庭和小企业，就像之前做过近 80 次一样。这是维持我们已经取得的经济进步的唯一途径，”他说。 </p></div><div class="article__quote-info"><div class="elem-info"><div class="elem-info__share"><div class="share" data-id="1110424452" data-url="https://sputnikglobe.com/20230517/congress-inaction-on-debt-limit-greatest-threat-to-us-economy-since-pandemic---treasury-1110424452.html?share-block=1110424455" data-title="&amp;quot;Congress must take action to raise the debt limit and do what is needed to protect families and small businesses, as it has done nearly 80 times before. It is the only way to maintain the economic progress we&amp;#x27;ve made,&amp;quot; he said."></div></div></div></div></div></div><div class="article__block" data-type="text"><div class="article__text">美国国会预算办公室上周警告称，如果立法者未能增加该国合法承担的债务数额，该国将在 6 月的前两周内面临违约的“重大风险”。</div></div></div> ]]>;</description><pubDate> Wed, 17 May 2023 17:54:28 GMT</pubDate><guid ispermalink="false"> https://sputniknews.com/20230517/congress-inaction-on-debt-limit-greatest-threat-to-us-economy-since-pandemic---treasury-1110424452.html</guid><link/> https://sputniknews.com/20230517/congress-inaction-on-debt-limit-greatest-threat-to-us-economy-since-pandemic---treasury-1110424452.html<category>美洲</category><category>美国债务上限危机</category><category>美国财政部</category><category>国会</category><category>美国国会</category><category>我们</category></item></channel></rss>